    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair, functional condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone looking for value. While it runs and drives well, there are visible signs of age including some clear coat fading on the hood and minor scuffs on the bumpers. The interior shows typical wear on the upholstery and a few non-essential electronic features are temperamental, but the engine and transmission remain solid. It\u2019s a dependable car that reflects its mileage and age honestly.",
