    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The exterior paint still holds a great luster, though you will find some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, shallow scratch on the passenger door consistent with regular use. The interior is clean and smoke-free, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a complete service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner.",
      "price": 33500.0,
